Key architectural decisions:
- Modular folder structure with well-defined layers
- Schema-first GraphQL using gqlgen
- Clean service / repository boundaries
- Strong typing, determinism in rollout logic, and desired test coverage
- HTTP / HTTPS as primary transport protocol

